Revision history for Fuse-Template

0.02     Sat Jun 19 13:37:00 CEST 2010
       * Fix dependencies
       * Add "ft" is alias for "self" in templates
       * Add more documentation
       * Change default values for gid() and uid()
       * Break backward compat: naming conventions for database results
         (tables) and columns default to "v7". (see
         http://search.cpan.org/dist/DBIx-Class-Schema-Loader/lib/DBIx/Class/Schema/Loader/Base.pm#naming
         for details)


0.01     Mon Jul 27 22:24:00 CET 2009
       * Add support for mount ro filesystem
       * Add support for templates
       * Add can read data from schema
         - Dynamic database schema load with DBIx::Class::Schema::Loader

